The camera is unre- sponsive.Temporary camera malfunction: Remove and reinsert the battery (□ 34). The battery is exhausted: Charge the battery or insert a ful- ly-charged spare battery (□ 37). The camera is connected to a wireless LAN: End the connec- tion. The controls are locked: Press and hold the MENU/OK button to unlock the controls ( � 1 1, 13).
The camera does not function as expected.Remove and reinsert the battery (□□ 34). If the problem persists, contact your Fujifilm dealer.
No sound.● Adjust the volume (□□ 275). OFF is selected for SOUND & FLASH: Select ON (□□ 274).
Pressing the Q button does not display the quick menu.TTL-LOCK is active: End TTL-LOCK (□□ 179).
